metadata.name: Taste me
metadata.description:
Feel the atmosphere. You enter the kitchen and see her. All around with flour, eggs, cream, and of course she is trying so hard to please you with a fragrant delicious pie. Almost everything is ready.

  To take this photo, I chose a wide angle lens. I wanted to round out the shape even more and make the photo even more attractive. 

Photo: 5079x6349 px
